query_string: above ground net primary production in a grassland in dimensions of biomass of plant material (with or without) (area or time)
grassland above ground net primary production
attribute:"net primary production" AND (abstract:"above ground" OR title:"above ground")
heterotrophic soil respiration as carbon dioxide flux in dimensions of (amount or mass) per (area or volume) per time
(attribute:"soil respiration" AND (attribute:"carbon dioxide" OR attribute:CO2) AND (attribute:time)) AND (abstract:heterotrophic OR title:heterotrophic) AND (abstract:soil OR title:soil)
soil carbon soil content in dimensions of (amount or mass) of carbon per (volume of soil or area of surface)
(attribute:carbon AND attribute:*gram*) AND (abstract:soil OR title: soil)
phytoplankton productivity as carbon increase in dimensions of (amount or mass) of carbon per (area or volume) per time
attribute:"productivity" AND (attribute:milligramPerMeterSquaredPerDay OR attribute:milligramPerMeterCubedPerDay) AND (abstract:phytoplankton OR title:phytoplankton)

column4: carbonate or bicarbonate in an aquatic system

query_string: attribute:concentration AND (attribute:"*carbonate" or attribute:"C02" or attribute:"carbon dioxide") AND (abstract:aquatic OR title:aquatic)
ecosystem carbon flux in dimensions of (amount or mass) of (carbon dioxide or carbon) per area per time
(attribute:"C02 flux" or attribute:"carbon dioxide flux") AND (abstract:"flux tower" OR title:"flux tower")
carbon dioxide uptake in an enrichment experiment in dimensions of (amount or mass) of carbon per (area or volume) per time
("C02 uptake" OR "carbon dioxide uptake") AND "enrichment experiment"
(attribute:"C02 uptake" or attribute:"carbon dioxide uptake") AND "enrichment experiment"
growth of trees measured as changes in (diameter
((attribute:diameter OR attribute:height OR attribute:circumference) AND attribute:date) AND (abstract:tree OR title:tree)
net primary production of coastal macroalgae in dimensions of (amount or mass) of carbon per area per time
attribute:"net primary production" AND (abstract:coastal macroalgae OR title:coastal macroalgae)
ocean carbon dioxide flux in dimensions of (amount or mass) of carbon per (area or volume) per time
(attribute:"C02 flux" or attribute:"carbon dioxide flux") AND (abstract:ocean OR title:ocean)
